   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Greetings, my lord brother Phanias. I put on board four . . . jars of old wine labelled 'Phanias". I trust that you long ago reminded Antonius Petron about the fifty drachmas (?). If not, write to him immediately so that the letter arrives before his departure. Also remind Asklepias who is sailing upriver about his fifty. I also put on board the ship which you sent up another three plants. How much do you want me (?) to buy?";Left margin: "To Phanias, secretary of the Harbor of Memphis (tax ?). Four jars."</ab>
         </div>
